msgid "This utility should only be used in live mode!"
msgstr "Ovaj alat bi trebao biti korišten samo u živom načinu rada!"

msgid ""
"<span font='12'>This tool should be used in live mode and to restore the Manjaro boot\n"
"installed on HD or SSD.</span>\n"
"\n"
"<span font='12' foreground='red'>If the installed system is starting correctly there are no "
"problems in the boot, so it is\n"
"better not to continue the use of this tool.</span>\n"
"<span font='10' foreground='gray'>Probably also work with other Linux distributions.</span>\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"Ovaj alat treba koristiti u živom načinu rada i za vraćanje Manjaro boot-a instaliranog na tvrdom "
"disku ili SSD-u.\n"
"\n"
"Ako instalirani sustav pokreće ispravno, nema problema s boot-om, pa je bolje ne nastavljati "
"upotrebu ovog alata.\n"
"\n"
"Vjerojatno će raditi i s drugim Linux distribucijama.\n"
"\n"
"Želite li nastaviti?"

msgid "Restore Boot, Grub, Initrd and others stuff"
msgstr "Vrati boot, grub, initrd i ostale stvari."

msgid "Wait..."
msgstr "Pričekaj..."

msgid "I didn't find any Linux installed on this computer, canceled process.\n"
msgstr "Nisam pronašao nijednu instaliranu linux na ovom računalu, otkazao sam proces."

msgid ""
"The boot in live mode is using EFI mode, but <span foreground='red'>I didn't find any EFI "
"partition</span> on this computer,\n"
"probably GRUB restoration will not work.\n"
"\n"
"Try to restart and through the computer BIOS make the boot in Legacy or BIOS mode.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to try even with little likely to work?"
msgstr ""
"\"Čizma u živom načinu rada koristi efi način, ali <span foreground='red'>nisam pronašao nijednu "
"efi particiju</span> na ovom računalu, vjerojatno obnova grub-a neće raditi.\n"
"\n"
"pokušajte ponovno pokrenuti računalo i putem biosa postaviti pokretanje u legacy ili bios načinu.\n"
"\n"
"želite li pokušati čak i ako je malo vjerojatno da će raditi?\""

msgid ""
"Boot in live mode is using Legacy mode, also called BIOS,\n"
"<span foreground='red'>but I found at least one EFI partition on this computer</span>,\n"
"probably GRUB restoration will not work.\n"
"\n"
"Try to restart and through the computer BIOS make the boot in EFI mode.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to try even with little likely to work?"
msgstr ""
"Pokretanje u živom načinu rada koristi legacy način, također nazvan bios,\n"
"<span foreground='red'>ali pronašao sam barem jednu efi particiju na ovom računalu</span>,\n"
"vjerovatno obnavljanje grub-a neće raditi.\n"
"\n"
"pokušajte ponovno pokrenuti računalo i putem bios-a postaviti pokretanje u efi načinu.\n"
"\n"
"želite li pokušati čak i ako je malo vjerojatno da će raditi?"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"\n"
"I found more than one EFI partition, select which one should use:"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='lightskyblue'>odaberite opciju:</span>\n"
"\n"
"Pronašao sam više od jedne EFI particije, odaberite koju želite koristiti:"

msgid "No EFI partition selected, canceled process."
msgstr "Nije odabrana EFI particija, proces je otkazan."

msgid "Restore the Boot, Grub and Initrd "
msgstr "Vrati boot, grub i initrd."

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"\n"
"I found more than one Linux installed on this computer, select which one should restore the boot:"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='lightskyblue'>odaberite opciju:</span>\n"
"\n"
"pronašao sam više od jednog instaliranog Linuxa na ovom računalu, odaberite koji bi trebao obnoviti "
"pokretanje:"

msgid "No selected partition, canceled process."
msgstr "Nema odabrane particije, prekinut proces."

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"    \n"
"I found more than one storage device, select which one should record the boot:"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='lightskyblue'>odaberite opciju:</span>\n"
"\n"
"pronašao sam više od jednog uređaja za pohranu, odaberite koji će snimati pokretanje:"

msgid "Disk"
msgstr "Disk"

msgid "Size"
msgstr "Veličina"

msgid "Name"
msgstr "Ime"

msgid "Partition table"
msgstr "Tablica particija"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Confirm the data:</span>    \n"
"\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Boot mode:</span>  LEGACY/BIOS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected disk:</span> $DISK_SELECTED\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Disk partition table:</span> $DISK_TABLE\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Disk Size:</span> $DISK_SIZE\n"
"   \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected partition:</span> $SELECTED_PARTITION\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected system:</span> $SELECTED_OS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition format:</span> $PARTITION_FORMAT\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition UUID:</span> $UUID_PARTITION\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"Potvrdite podatke:\n"
"\n"
"Način pokretanja:\n"
"legacy/bios\n"
"Odabrani disk: $disk_selected\n"
"\n"
"Tablica particija diska: $disk_table\n"
"\n"
"Veličina diska: $disk_size\n"
"\n"
"Odabrana particija: $selected_partition\n"
"Odabrani sustav: $selected_os\n"
"Format particije: $partition_format\n"
"UUID particije: $uuid_partition\n"
"\n"
"Želite li nastaviti?"

msgid "Your computer is not connected to the internet, options 2 and 3 need internet to work."
msgstr "Vaše računalo nije povezano s internetom, opcije 2 i 3 zahtijevaju internet za rad."

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select the desired option:</span>\n"
"        \n"
"Restoration can be done in 3 ways (<span foreground='gray'>Simple, Intermediate or "
"Complete</span>),if in doubt, try the first\n"
"option, restart the computer and see if you resolved.\n"
"\n"
"If the problem persists try the other options."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite željenu opciju:\n"
"\n"
"Obnova se može izvršiti na 3 načina (<span foreground='gray'>jednostavno, srednje ili "
"potpuno</span>), ako ste u nedoumici, pokušajte prvu opciju, ponovno pokrenite računalo i "
"provjerite jeste li riješili problem.\n"
"\n"
"Ako se problem nastavi, pokušajte s drugim opcijama."

msgid "Option"
msgstr "Opcija"

msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

msgid "Simple, just record the grub again at the beginning of the disk."
msgstr "Jednostavno, samo ponovno snimite grub na početku diska."

msgid ""
"Intermediate, reinstalls the GRUB package in the partition, generates the configuration and updates "
"Initrd."
msgstr "Srednji, ponovno instalira paket grub u particiji, generira konfiguraciju i ažurira initrd."

msgid ""
"Complete, performs the stages of the intermediate restoration, updates the system and checks if the "
"LTS kernel is installed."
msgstr "Završi, izvršava faze srednje obnove, ažurira sustav i provjerava je li instaliran lts kernel."

msgid "Interactive, opens a terminal within the selected system."
msgstr "Interaktivno, otvara terminal unutar odabranog sustava."

msgid "Interactive, opens a TUI control center within the selected system."
msgstr "Interaktivno, otvara tui kontrolni centar unutar odabranog sustava."

msgid "Collect useful logs from installed system."
msgstr "Sakupljajte korisne zapise iz instaliranog sustava."

msgid "Interactive, opens the package manager within the selected system."
msgstr "Interaktivno, otvara upravitelja paketa unutar odabranog sustava."

msgid "Restore System with Timeshift ( only if Timeshift is configurated )"
msgstr "Vrati sustav pomoću timeshifta (samo ako je timeshift konfiguriran)."

msgid "Done!"
msgstr "Gotovo!"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Confirm the data:</span>\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Boot mode:</span> EFI\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>EFI partition:</span> $EFI_PARTITION\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected partition:</span> $SELECTED_PARTITION\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected system:</span> $SELECTED_OS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition format:</span> $PARTITION_FORMAT\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition UUID:</span> $UUID_PARTITION\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"Potvrdite podatke:\n"
"\n"
"Način pokretanja: efi\n"
"Particija efi: $efi_partition\n"
"\n"
"Odabrana particija: $selected_partition\n"
"Odabrani sustav: $selected_os\n"
"Format particije: $partition_format\n"
"UUID particije: $uuid_partition\n"
"\n"
"Želite li nastaviti?"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select the desired option:</span>\n"
"        \n"
"Restoration can be done in 3 ways(<span foreground='gray'>Simple, Intermediate or Complete</span>), "
"if in doubt, try the first\n"
"option, restart the computer and see if you resolved.\n"
"\n"
"If the problem persists try the other options."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite željenu opciju:\n"
"\n"
"Obnova se može izvršiti na 3 načina (<span foreground='gray'>jednostavno, srednje ili "
"potpuno</span>), ako ste u nedoumici, pokušajte prvu opciju, ponovno pokrenite računalo i "
"provjerite jeste li riješili problem.\n"
"\n"
"Ako se problem nastavi, pokušajte s drugim opcijama."

msgid "Timeshift not installed!"
msgstr "Timeshift nije instaliran!"
